Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.25,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The time has come...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:03.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,for our company to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:05.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,to start restructuring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:07.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Does this mean that I can quit early?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:08.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Plus, the retirement benefits will be increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's only for employees over 50, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:12.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So I can't take up this offer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to retire early that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:15.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,While the salary goes up, the performance goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:21.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All the older employees who represents a negative legacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:25.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,the company cuts them off by offering them retirement benefits that coincide with the time when they're still able to pursue their second career.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:28.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that it's a very rational move for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you say all of that to our three crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not rational at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:36.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So you do understand what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:37.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I had an awakening the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wonder who will take up the offer to retire early?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yamauchi of the Safety Management Department,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:47.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it seems like he's really into making {\i1}soba{\i0} with his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:51.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Retire and then open up a restaurant, the best case scenario, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:52.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's yellow light for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:57.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And my classmate Sudo, it seems like he's been watching youtube videos about investments lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:00:59.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is a red light for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But we're going to cling to this company with both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:05.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I won't let go, don't you agree, Kijimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:09.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:20.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The parts are way too detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Space Battleship Yamato 2202, the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:42.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Those tiny parts are just like the countless stars in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Building the Yamato is quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I suddenly raised the difficulty way too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:48.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If Shinji was able to do it, there's no way that you couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You got heated looking at Shinji-san's Eva, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:55.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Get fired up, Zakunee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All of this for the cannons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Those tiny parts are delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The impact of cutting it with a nipper might break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gently cut it off using that cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:08.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm scared because I might break it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the trauma from building the Zaku, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Assembling it is only the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The real battle lies ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it can fly to space or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's going to fly using the wave engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Assembling it is only the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Are you thinking about where to go for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:31.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I brought my own lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:36.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you to come up with a new goods idea for Manten Nodoame-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Idea for new goods? \N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Inuzuka-kun, that is something that I do every year...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for not noticing it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:42.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:45.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We should leave this kind of work to the young generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:45.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:50.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As the Acting Chief, it's more than enough for you to just oversee things as an observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Komukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Observer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, go say something to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san, I'm honored to be working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's Kijimura behind Manten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Learn from him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:02.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:04.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Like an observer, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko and Kijimura-san teaming up is so unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The oldest employee in the Events Department, Acting Chief Kijimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:11.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even when Inuzuka-san, who was once his junior,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,passed him and became his boss, he's still chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I also want to be someone as prideless as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't actually think so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good analysis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:27.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you think that we should go the same route as last year's comfy cushion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, I think that a new project might be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A new project?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Like bath salts from Manten Herb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that a no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:41.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The client loved last year's goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't have to change route.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I will take the same route as last years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:47.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:55.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, I slept in the train and have arrived at \NTobu Zoological Park, which is on the exact opposite direction from our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You even came to an amazing place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:59.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've been staying up late lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:00.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks like that I won't make it in time for the presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do the presentation instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm praying for your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's going to be okay, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cushy pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:19.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a pillow that can make you feel the relaxing sensation of Manten Nodoame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't this basically the same thing as last year's cushy cushion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The theme for this year is a good night sleep, so we went with a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a brand new project instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A brand new project?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The feedback that we got from the customers last year was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that we should go with this for this year's goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you sure going with that project?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:54.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san has been working with this company longer than me, so we must tread carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,30 years was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard that some of our board members is indebted to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Old kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, Kijimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:16.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How was the presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They accepted the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The cushy pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:24.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,As expected from "There's Kijimura behind Manten".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:28.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it, I didn't do anything that was praiseworthy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:29.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you about something, Kijimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,About the product exhibition at Kirari Mall,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,there are talks that Shinji and I will be taking over this year's event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Why all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a work that requires strength, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:53.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel bad to leave this work to you every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't think that is true though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We young people should be the ones who put our bodies to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I leave it to you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll whip Shinji into shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please switch places with me, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:25.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,President.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that, we're classmates after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I mean, the president is the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard that you're still in charge of Manten-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That sure bring back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's been 30 years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:51.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please let FUNFUN CREATE be in charge of the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They were the first client that we secured, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's been 30 years since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:06.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who didn't change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:10.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Being in charge of one client for that long is an amazing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:14.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,People around me is being considerate because I'm old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:21.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's sad without you in the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:52.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the acting chief, it's more than enough for you to just oversee things as an observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kijimura-san has been working with this company longer than me, so we must tread carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We young people should be the ones who put our bodies to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:07.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Early Retirement Application Form]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess it's time to move on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:23.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you going to the usual place again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:28.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, but I'm exhausted because it's super difficult delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Since when have you become a plastic model mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:38.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai-san, could it be that you are currently building the Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:43.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:51.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that there's a model shop close to the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I found this place by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Zakunee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:03.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Who did you bring along today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Komukai-san's colleague, Kijimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He wanted to come after I told him about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Same generation as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:12.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Old men are welcomed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:19.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is so nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:23.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was a modeller back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? I couldn't tell at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:30.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was so into it for a time, that my wife gave me an earful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That happens quite a lot to a modeller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:32.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you build Gunplas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I mainly built ships or boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A scale model specialist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yassan is in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,These are quite the tiny parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:54.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm clumsy, I managed to get this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No no, you did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's all thank to my support.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's better if you didn't say that out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:03.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you have an idea of how you want to paint it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:09.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it's Yamato, I wanted it to look strong, cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:10.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can't imagine what comes after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:16.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You've hit the imagination wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Imagination wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:30.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have a vague idea of what you want to do, but you don't have the details drawer to pull it out from.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:31.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A drawer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He said something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with Space Battleship Yamato in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can sing the chorus of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:51.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In the year of 2199, humanity is one year away from extinction due to radiation contamination that was caused by an alien invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:59.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Humanity used the wave engine that was brought by the Queen of the Iscandar and installed it to the battleship Yamato that was sunk during the Pacific war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:04.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Space Battleship Yamato tells the story of the journey to the planet Iscandar to retrieve a device that can cleanse the Earth of its radiation damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He said the same thing as Yassan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:11.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It is important to imagine what battles Yamato went through as it traveled through the vastness of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:14.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and to express that using paint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not the usual Kijimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The real deal has come to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:20.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:22.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you're willing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,do you mind helping me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:32.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to get over the imagination wall together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then I would like to everything starting from the basecoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:41.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, I can't finish the whole thing in just one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's a veteran for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't this basically the same thing as last year's cushy cushion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't you have a brand new project instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, I think that a new project might be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:02.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's try something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is that you're using?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:17.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Smooth clear spray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:21.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It removes the gloss characteristic of plastic models and creates a rough surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:27.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This way, we don't have to paint everything and make use of it's original color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So we can enjoy the colors of the original materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He sure knows his stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:35.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's common knowledge for a modeller.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're so hard on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next, is the filter liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're using that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:11.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Then by wiping the painted parts like this, it gives the plastic model a refined look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:12.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A refined look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It means making it look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's do it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next up is rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Would you like to do the honors, Komukai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:50.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How do you paint rust again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:51.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:57.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Rust actually erodes gradually from these metal-to-metal joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:01.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So you have to paint it while imagining the natural phenomenon that occurs in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that I can picture it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is what is called the imagination wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that you can do today, Yassan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:28.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture the things that the Yamato has been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is also how the pros do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I love doing things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:32.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I entered this line of work with the intention of doing scenography for theme parks and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:37.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I only want to enjoy going to theme parks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,there was only 5 of us working for the company back in the day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and so I was so busy getting the jobs that were in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:59.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,At that time, the first client that I and the current President managed to secure
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,was Manten Nodoame-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The President and you are classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was a daredevil back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A daredevil? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:11.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine it at all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:19.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You always honest, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:22.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's great hearing that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:40.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Lastly, let's peel off the masking tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's going to be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:51.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Space Battleship Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:40.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can see what the Yamato has been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:05.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The dirty Kijimura has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have a knack for this, Komukai-san
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:11.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to pass the imagination wall again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:16.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Painting is not just about coloring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:22.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Imagine just what kind of adventures that this 1/1000 scale of Yamato has actually been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:25.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,the goal is to get close to what we have in mind as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It is truly the ultimate imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:31.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:34.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:35.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:39.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see that you also get fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:45.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Kijimura the Buddha now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:49.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've remembered the good old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to build another plastic model with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If the opportunity arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Kijimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want him to be the leader for this project.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not a project that an Acting Chief should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to work with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:16.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By the way, why are you being so considerate towards Kijimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:19.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, he's the oldest person here and it's not like I'm being considerate or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's the harm then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If he wants to do it then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,By the way, it's rare seeing you this assertive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:26.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:35.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a floral event in Tokyo, I'd like to ask you to supervise the entire decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:37.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why are you coming to me once again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The Yamato was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's only a plastic model.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"The spirit of craftsmanship works on anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yassan said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:53.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, doing this work after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it because you're an Acting Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:04.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The Acting Chief is only my title.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:12.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:15.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A new plastic model.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you build that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:20.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I got Kijimura-san to help me build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see that you also build plastic models, Kijimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was my hobby back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:26.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm currently making a character figurine for our client with Nakano-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,but we can't get the color of the sample just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let me see that. \N-Here you go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:45.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is due to the undercoating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:46.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Undercoating?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:47.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:54.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The process of undercoating is to ensure that the topcoat adheres properly to the surface of the material.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:56.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This sample seems to have skipped that step.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:22:00.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If it's okay with you, will you come with us to the factory to check it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:01.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:02.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:06.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:10.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The young ones loves Kijimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You and Kijimura-san have different social skills after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:14.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:15.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was rude of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:17.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Rude? Does that mean that you meant it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:19.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:21.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:22.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:24.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:26.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at this color sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:27.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:29.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,After you spray the sub,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:31.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I mean the undercoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:35.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,After that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:37.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,